# Whisky Hikes Testing & Mock Setup Guide

## Overview
Diese Regel beschreibt die Test-Architektur und Mock-Setups für das Whisky Hikes Projekt, insbesondere für Postgres/Supabase-Integration.

## Test Structure

### Directory Organization
```
test/
├── config/           # Test-Konfiguration
├── data/            # Data Layer Tests
├── domain/          # Domain Model Tests
├── integration/     # End-to-End Tests
├── mocks/           # Mock-Definitionen
├── repositories/    # Repository Tests
├── services/        # Service Tests
├── UI/              # UI Component Tests
├── test_helpers.dart # Zentrale Test-Hilfsfunktionen
└── run_all_tests.dart # Test-Runner
```

### Mock Files Location
- **Mock Definitions**: `test/mocks/mock_*.dart`
- **Generated Mocks**: `test/mocks/mock_*.mocks.dart`
- **Test Helpers**: `test/test_helpers.dart`

## Mock Setup Configuration

### 1. Supabase Mocks
**File**: `test/mocks/mock_supabase.dart`

```dart
@GenerateMocks([
  SupabaseClient,
  SupabaseQueryBuilder,
  PostgrestFilterBuilder,
  PostgrestBuilder,
  SupabaseStorageClient,
  StorageFileApi,
  GoTrueClient,
  User,
  Bucket,
  FileObject,
])
```

**Verwendung in Tests**:
```dart
import 'package:whisky_hikes/test/mocks/mock_supabase.dart';

void main() {
  late MockSupabaseClient mockSupabase;
  
  setUp(() {
    mockSupabase = MockSupabaseClient();
  });
}
```

### 2. Repository Mocks
**File**: `test/mocks/mock_repositories.dart`

```dart
@GenerateMocks([
  HikeRepository,
  ProfileRepository,
  WaypointRepository,
  CompanyRepository,
])
```

### 3. Service Mocks
**File**: `test/mocks/mock_backend_api_service.dart`

```dart
@GenerateMocks([BackendApiService])
```

## Test Data Creation

### Test Helpers
**File**: `test/test_helpers.dart`

```dart
class TestHelpers {
  static List<Hike> createSampleHikes() { ... }
  static List<Profile> createSampleProfiles() { ... }
  static List<Waypoint> createSampleWaypoints(int hikeId) { ... }
  
  // Factory Methods für einzelne Test-Objekte
  static Hike createTestHike({...}) { ... }
  static Profile createTestProfile({...}) { ... }
  static Waypoint createTestWaypoint({...}) { ... }
}
```

### Verwendung in Tests
```dart
void main() {
  test('should create hike with valid data', () {
    final hike = TestHelpers.createTestHike(
      id: 1,
      name: 'Test Hike',
      length: 5.0,
    );
    
    expect(hike.id, equals(1));
    expect(hike.name, equals('Test Hike'));
  });
}
```

## Mock Setup Best Practices

### 1. Setup in setUp()
```dart
void main() {
  late MockHikeRepository mockHikeRepository;
  late MockSupabaseClient mockSupabase;
  
  setUp(() {
    mockHikeRepository = MockHikeRepository();
    mockSupabase = MockSupabaseClient();
    
    // Standard-Mock-Verhalten definieren
    when(mockHikeRepository.getAllHikes())
        .thenAnswer((_) async => TestHelpers.createSampleHikes());
  });
}
```

### 2. Mock-Verhalten definieren
```dart
// Erfolgreicher Fall
when(mockRepository.getHike(1))
    .thenAnswer((_) async => TestHelpers.createTestHike(id: 1));

// Fehlerfall
when(mockRepository.getHike(999))
    .thenThrow(Exception('Hike not found'));

// Async-Operationen
when(mockRepository.saveHike(any))
    .thenAnswer((_) async => true);
```

### 3. Verifizierung von Mock-Aufrufen
```dart
test('should call repository method', () async {
  await viewModel.loadHikes();
  
  verify(mockHikeRepository.getAllHikes()).called(1);
  verifyNever(mockHikeRepository.getHike(any));
});
```

## Common Testing Patterns

### 1. ViewModel Tests
```dart
void main() {
  late HikeViewModel viewModel;
  late MockHikeRepository mockRepository;
  
  setUp(() {
    mockRepository = MockHikeRepository();
    viewModel = HikeViewModel(repository: mockRepository);
  });
  
  test('should load hikes successfully', () async {
    final hikes = TestHelpers.createSampleHikes();
    when(mockRepository.getAllHikes()).thenAnswer((_) async => hikes);
    
    await viewModel.loadHikes();
    
    expect(viewModel.hikes, equals(hikes));
    expect(viewModel.isLoading, isFalse);
    expect(viewModel.error, isNull);
  });
}
```

### 2. Repository Tests
```dart
void main() {
  late HikeRepositoryImpl repository;
  late MockSupabaseClient mockSupabase;
  
  setUp(() {
    mockSupabase = MockSupabaseClient();
    repository = HikeRepositoryImpl(supabase: mockSupabase);
  });
  
  test('should fetch hikes from Supabase', () async {
    final mockQuery = MockSupabaseQueryBuilder();
    when(mockSupabase.from('hikes')).thenReturn(mockQuery);
    when(mockQuery.select()).thenReturn(mockQuery);
    when(mockQuery.execute()).thenAnswer((_) async => MockResponse());
    
    await repository.getAllHikes();
    
    verify(mockSupabase.from('hikes')).called(1);
  });
}
```

## Troubleshooting

### 1. Mock Generation Issues
```bash
# Mocks neu generieren
flutter pub run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs

# Nur Mocks generieren
flutter pub run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs --build-filter=mockito
```

### 2. Common Mock Errors
- **"NoSuchMethodError"**: Mock wurde nicht korrekt generiert
- **"Mock not found"**: Import der Mock-Datei fehlt
- **"Method not stubbed"**: Mock-Verhalten wurde nicht definiert

### 3. Test Setup Issues
- **"Test not found"**: Test-Datei hat nicht die Endung `_test.dart`
- **"Compilation failed"**: Freezed-Modelle müssen neu generiert werden
- **"Mock not working"**: `setUp()` wird nicht korrekt ausgeführt

## Integration Test Setup

### 1. Test Environment
```dart
// test/integration/setup.dart
import 'package:flutter_test/flutter_test.dart';
import 'package:whisky_hikes/main.dart' as app;

void main() {
  IntegrationTestWidgetsFlutterBinding.ensureInitialized();
  
  group('App Integration Tests', () {
    testWidgets('should navigate through app', (tester) async {
      app.main();
      await tester.pumpAndSettle();
      
      // Test-Logik hier
    });
  });
}
```

### 2. Mock Services in Integration Tests
```dart
// Services für Integration Tests mocken
setUpAll(() {
  // Globale Mock-Setups
